{"id": "art-116", "label": "Art. 116", "title": "Art. 116", "slug": "art-116", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1329767744\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2326\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1329767744\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 116 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Hot&#259;rârea\nunei adun&#259;ri generale de a modifica drepturile sau <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iile</span>\nreferitoare la o categorie de <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> nu produce\nefecte decât în urma aprob&#259;rii acestei hot&#259;râri de c&#259;tre\nadunarea special&#259; a <span class=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torilor</span> de <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> din acea categorie.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)<span class=SpellE>Dispozi&#355;iile</span>\nprezentei <span class=SpellE>sec&#355;iuni</span> privind convocarea, cvorumul <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>desf&#259;&#351;urarea</span>\nadun&#259;rilor generale ale <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span> se\naplic&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> adun&#259;rilor speciale.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)Hot&#259;rârile <span\nclass=SpellE>ini&#355;iate</span> de adun&#259;rile speciale vor fi supuse\naprob&#259;rii adun&#259;rilor generale corespunz&#259;toare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>*) În interpretarea <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> aplicarea <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span>\nart. 132 din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> nr. 31/1990, republicat&#259;, cu\nmodific&#259;rile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> complet&#259;rile\nulterioare, raportat la art. 116 din <span class=SpellE>aceea&#351;i</span> <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i>, pot fi atacate în <span\nclass=SpellE>justi&#355;ie</span>, cu <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iune</span> în\nanulare, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> hot&#259;rârile adoptate de adunarea\nspecial&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}